### Description of Issue/Question
If telegram bot have an edited message beacons do not work anymore
Error in minion log:

AttributeError: 'NoneType' object has no attribute 'chat'

I've already open an issue here:
https://github.com/python-telegram-bot/python-telegram-bot/issues/1244

### Setup
beacons:
  telegram_bot_msg:
    - token: "XXXX:XXXXXXXX"
    - accept_from:
      - "XXXXX"
    - interval: 50

### Steps to Reproduce Issue
Edit message with the telegram bot.

